<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="M" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Mane" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Mane,</orth> the hair growing on the necks of horses and lions: <bibl n="shak. ven 271" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 271</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ven 271" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 271</bibl> <bibl n="shak. tro 3.3.224" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. III, 3, 224</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 1.4.89" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. I, 4, 89</bibl>. Used of the foaming crest of waves: <bibl n="shak. oth 2.1.13" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. II, 1, 13</bibl>. In <bibl n="shak. aww 4.5.41" default="NO" valid="yes">All's IV, 5, 41</bibl> O. Edd. <emph>main,</emph> M. Edd. <emph>name.</emph>
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>